18... Rae8+ 19. Ne3 Re4 { Dark clouds are hanging over White's position! } 20.
d4 Ng2+ 21. Kd1 Rxe3 22. Bxe3 Nxe3+ 23. Kc1 Bd6
{ White's king isn't out of the woods just yet. Apart from that there is no coordination between Whites forces whatsoever. }
