20... Nf3+ 21. Rxf3 Qxf3 22. dxc5 Rxe3+ 23. Nxe3 Qxe3+ 24. Kf1 Qf3+ 25. Kg1
Qg4+ { With a perpetual, is a likely outcome. } *

