{ 16...Qh3+  17.Kxf4  transposes to16.Kg3. } 17. Bf1 Qd5+ 18. Kg3
{ 18.Re4  Re8!  19.d3  f5  wins the rook, with an ongoing attack. } 18... Nh5+
19. Kg4 f5+ { The mating net closes. } 20. Kxh5 Qf7+ 21. Kxg5 Qg6+ 22. Kf4 Qg4+
23. Ke5 Re8+ 24. Kf6 Qg6# *

