10. O-O O-O 11. Kh1
{ White sidesteps the king in order to push f2-f4. Not a bad idea in itself, but we are ready for it. }
11... d6 12. f4 f5 13. Be3
{ Instead,  13.exf5  Bxf5  14.Qd1  Rae8  is already excellent for Black. }
13... Qa5
{ 13...Qxb2  14.a3!  is dangerous. But after the text move the position is dynamically equal. }
*

